<div class="envType">
	<h3>Choose your environment type</h3>

	<div class="text-center col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		<div class="environmentBox" ng-class="{'selectedEnv': envType==='manual'}" ng-click="switchEnv('manual')">
			<img ng-if="0" ng-src="" height="32" class="f-left"/>
			<h4>Development environment</h4>
			<hr>
			<div class="envDescription">I want to create a development environment
			</div>
			<p class="fieldMsg">
				Create a blank environment and handle deployment manually.<br>
				Good for testing
			</p>
			<div class="readmore clearfix">
				<a><span class="icon icon-info"></span></a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="text-center col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		<div class="environmentBox" ng-class="{'selectedEnv': envType==='singleInfra'}" ng-click="switchEnv('singleInfra')">
			<div style="font-size: 28px; padding: 3px; padding-left: 6px;" class="f-left">
				<span style="color: #337ab7;" class="icon icon-cloud"></span>
			</div>
			<h4>Single cloud environment</h4>
			<hr>
			<div class="envDescription">I want to create an environment and deploy it on a single infra
			</div>
			<p class="fieldMsg">
				Your container deployment is restricted to one cloud provider;
				1 cloud provider per container cluster.<br>
				If you choose only one provider, you can communicate using the private IP.<br>
				You can have different clusters on different providers and communicate among them via public IP.
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>One cluster per provider</li>
				<li>Communication via public IP</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="readmore clearfix">
				<a><span class="icon icon-info"></span></a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="text-center col-md-4 col-lg-4">
		<div class="environmentBox noHover" ng-class="{'selectedEnv': envType==='multiInfra'}" ng-click="">
			<div class="f-left">
				<img ng-src="modules/dashboard/environments/images/multiCloud.png" height="32"/>
			</div>
			<h4>Multi cloud environment</h4>
			<hr>
			<div class="envDescription">I want to create an environment and deploy it on multiple infra
			</div>
			<p class="fieldMsg">
				Your container deployment is on multiple providers
			</p>
			<ul style="">
				<li>Cluster on more than one provider</li>
				<li>Communication via private IP</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="readmore clearfix">
				<a><span class="icon icon-info"></span></a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="clearfix"></div>
<br>
<hr>
<div ng-if="showTemplates">
	<h3>Choose a Template</h3>

	<div ng-repeat="template in templates">

		<div class="text-center col-md-4 col-lg-4">

			<div class="environmentBox" ng-click="chooseTemplate(template);">
				<img ng-if="template.logo" ng-src="{{template.logo}}" height="32" class="f-left"/>
				<h4>{{template.name}}</h4>
				<hr>
				<p class="fieldMsg">{{template.description}}
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
